ecay via TrustMath.expDecay()   - EMA smoothing via TrustMath.ema()   - Cooldown: 1 attestation per target per epoch Patent Family B: Runtime governance of learning/adaptive systems.\",\"errors\":{\"OwnableInvalidOwner(address)\":[{\"details\":\"The owner is not a valid owner account. (eg. `address(0)`)\"}],\"OwnableUnauthorizedAccount(address)\":[{\"details\":\"The caller account is not authorized to perform an operation.\"}]},\"kind\":\"dev\",\"methods\":{\"getTrustScore(bytes32)\":{\"params\":{\"nodeId\":\"The node to query.\"},\"returns\":{\"_0\":\"score  Weighted median trust score (WAD).\"}},\"getTrustWeightedVote(bytes32)\":{\"details\":\"Returns trustScore directly \\u2014 GovernanceDAO applies the full formula.\",\"params\":{\"nodeId\":\"The node to query.\"},\"returns\":{\"_0\":\"vote   The trust-weighted vote (WAD).\"}},\"owner()\":{\"details\":\"Returns the address of the current owner.\"},\"renounceOwnership()\":{\"details\":\"Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.\"},\"reportTrust(bytes32,uint256,bytes)\":{\"details\":\"Caller must own a registered node. One attestation per target per epoch.\",\"params\":{\"targetNodeId\":\"The node being assessed.\",\"trustScore\":\"Trust score in WAD (0 to 1e18). Accepts a third bytes parameter reserved for future ECDSA verification.\"}},\"transferOwnership(address)\":{\"details\":\"Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.\"}},\"stateVariables\":{\"lastAttestEpoch\":{\"details\":\"Cooldown: reporter => target => last epoch attested\"}},\"title\":\"TrustOracle\",\"version\":1},\"userdoc\":{\"kind\":\"user\",\"methods\":{\"BLOCKS_PER_EPOCH()\":{\"notice\":\"Blocks per epoch for attestation cooldown.\"},\"MAX_ATTESTATIONS()\